      • getPopup

        protected org.openqa.selenium.WebElement getPopup()
        Some DOJO combo-box has an associated popup-menu, which can be used to select/click/count item.
        This function will click the combo-box's button to load and show the associated popup-menu, then
        find the popup-menu.
        Returns:
        WebElement, the popup-menu associated with this combo-box.

      • dojo_HasDropDown_isLoaded

        protected boolean dojo_HasDropDown_isLoaded()
        Some Dojo Combo-box (dijit.form.ComboBox, dijit.form.Select etc.) contains a drop-down menu,
        but the drop-down will not be loaded until you trigger it by click the combo-box-button or calling
        combo-box API. This method is used to test if the associated drop-down has been shown or not.
        Returns:
        boolean, true if the associated drop-down menu has been loaded.

      • dojo_HasDropDown_loadAndOpenDropDown

        protected boolean dojo_HasDropDown_loadAndOpenDropDown()
        Some Dojo Combo-box (dijit.form.ComboBox, dijit.form.Select etc.) contains a drop-down menu,
        but the drop-down will not be loaded until you trigger it by click the combo-box-button or calling
        combo-box API. This method is used to load the drop-down menu and open it.
        Returns:
        boolean, true if the associated drop-down menu has been successfully loaded.
